Subject: [PATCH 096/631] sched/alt: [Sync] f2469a1fb43f sched/core: Wait for
 tasks being pushed away on hotplug

---
 kernel/sched/alt_core.c  | 162 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
